					&lt;source&gt;8&lt;/source&gt;
					&lt;target&gt;8&lt;/target&gt;
				&lt;/configuration&gt;
			&lt;/plugin&gt;
		&lt;/plugins&gt;
	&lt;/build&gt;

now **intelliJ** 2019.3 CE does this for you if you go to import then alt+enter where you will get an option saying &quot;change language level to 8 to use this functionality&quot;

